<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="111">
This new genus currently includes a single species. However, future investigation may prove that 
<taxonomicName authority="BechynÃ©, 1956" authorityName="Moura" authorityYear="2003" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Zischkaita" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zischkaita serrana" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="serrana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Zischkaita serrana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Moura also belongs here, although it is a much less slender beetle. The male front legs of 
<taxonomicName genus="Z." lsidName="Z. serrana" pageId="0" pageNumber="111" rank="species" species="serrana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Z. serrana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
exhibit modifications very similar to those of 
<taxonomicName authority="Viswajyothi &amp; Clark, 2020" authorityName="Viswajyothi &amp; Clark" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Prathapanius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Prathapanius" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Prathapanius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, except that the femoral enlargement is not nearly as dramatic (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1590/S0101-81752003000400014" author="Moura, L" journalOrPublisher="Revista Brasileira de Zoologia" pageId="0" pageNumber="111" pagination="643 - 645" refId="B10" refString="Moura, L, 2003. Nova especie de Zischkaita Bechyne e notas taxonomicas em Galerucini (Coleoptera, Chrysomelidae, Galerucinae). Revista Brasileira de Zoologia 20 (4): 643 - 645, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1590/S0101-81752003000400014" title="Nova especie de Zischkaita Bechyne e notas taxonomicas em Galerucini (Coleoptera, Chrysomelidae, Galerucinae)." url="https://doi.org/10.1590/S0101-81752003000400014" volume="20" year="2003">Moura 2003</bibRefCitation>
). The original description of 
<taxonomicName genus="Z." lsidName="Z. serrana" pageId="0" pageNumber="111" rank="species" species="serrana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="111">Z. serrana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
does not mention the genal length or genitalia, and we have not examined specimens.
</paragraph>
